data.description: Seller to give closing cost assistance with full price offer. Discover this fully renovated Norfolk gem on a dead-end street, minutes from highways, military bases, and the airport. The first floor boasts a seamless open layout featuring elegant hardwood laminate flooring. Revel in a brand-new kitchen, complete with pristine white cabinets, stainless steel appliances, a deep sink, granite countertops, and a high-quality commercial-style spring faucet. This space effortlessly flows into a formal dining area, with a conveniently adjacent office area. Ascend the stairs to the second floor, where you'll find three well-appointed bedrooms, including the primary bedroom with an en-suite bathroom featuring a fully tiled shower. This home is practically new, from the roof to the windows and the outdoor HVAC system. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home. Visit today!
